                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8213" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2051</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2047 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从卖场“老将”到数字化“领头羊”——HC公司的数字化之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Traditional Store Leader to Digital Pioneer HC Company&#39;s Digitalization Journey</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王婷，于颖，犹伟，何跃勇，聂文倩，陈美晶</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贵州大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">昆明市居然之家家居建材市场有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">6 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家居连锁企业；数字化；战略转型；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Home Furnishing Chain Enterprises; Digitalization; Strategic Transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字技术的快速发展和新零售模式的不断普及，给传统家居流通业带来了巨大的冲击，通过数字科技赋能家装行业存在巨大的机遇与空间。本案例描述了HC公司作为行业龙头企业的数字化转型历程。十年间，HC公司在不同阶段尝试抓住时代热点进行数字化转型，受挫时及时进行战略调整，最终抓住新零售的风口，转型初见成效。本案例旨在帮助学员理解数字化转型的内涵，使用战略理论工具分析企业转型的动因，从核心竞争力的视角思考数字化转型，了解新零售发展现状和未来趋势，提高学员的战略选择能力和环境应变能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The rapid development of digital technology and the continuous popularization of new retail models have brought huge impacts to the traditional home circulation industry while generated enormous opportunities and space for empowering for home decoration industry through digital technology. This case elaborates the Digital transformation process of HC Company as a leading enterprise in the industry. Over the course of ten years, HC attempted digital transformation at different stages, seizing opportunities in line with the trends of the times, making strategic adjustments when faced with setbacks, and eventually capitalizing on the new retail trend, leading to initial success in their transformation. This case aims to help students improve knowledge of the digital transformation essence, using strategic theory tools to analyze the driving forces behind enterprise transformation, reflect on digital transformation from the perspective of core competitiveness, comprehend the current status and future trends of new retail development, and improve students&#39; strategic choice ability and environmental adaptability.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型的概念以及驱动因素；核心竞争力理论；数字化转型的方法与措施；新零售的发展现状与未来趋势；战略选择</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-03</td>
                            </tr>
